== Door entry system ==
''Entryphone is a registered trademark''


An intercom system fitted at the entrance to a building, especially a block of flats, by which visitors can identify themselves to specific occupants before being admitted to the building.

The Entryphone Company Limitd, holders of the Entryphone trade mark has been supplying and installing door entry systems since 1958.  

